    "Anthropomorphizing human-like simulacra can be a useful shorthand, assisting us in predicting their behavior, in contrast to anthropomorphizing language models themselves [2].",
    "That leads us to the primary focus of this article: To what extent can we effectively employ LLMs to simulate personas characterized by limited cognitive capacities?",
